>Perhaps ioremap() does not work properly on arm.
In fact it does.  It does also so happen that, on the ARM architecture where 
Cyber2000 is most commonly used, bus_to_virt() happens to yield the right 
answer too.  Whether this is a good or bad thing is debatable.
